# A few sites with trouble MS windows application in general.
[link1](https://www.maketecheasier.com)

Make tech easier offers an article which includes a list of frequent issues in windows 10 and 11.
Website explains each and every point according to problem and also asuggest tips.

Link-2 (https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/)
Geeksforgeeks Website has an artile called (7 common window errors and how to fix them) which explains problems lile apps not responding etc. and give step by step solutions to fix them 

link-3 (https://support.microsoft.com/en-us)
Microsoft support provides an official troubleshooters that can diagnose and resolve verios system issues .


# 3 sites that are tutorials on Windows File Explorer .

Link-1  (https://support.microsoft.com/en-us)
Microsoft support provides an official guides and tipas that how to use File exp in windows 10 and 11 .
It covers the features like sharing files and changing them .


Link-2 (https://www.thewindowsclub.com/)
The windows club offers a guide on how to using file exp. in windows 10,11 and also includes methods to open its components and custmization options .


Link -3 (https://www.techradar.com/)
Tech radar provide tutorial on using file explorar in windows and provide tips for manage files .

According to my opnion Microsoft support is best option for begniners to get knowledge about windows. Because it provides the solution for problems whcih are linked to windows . 
